      "content": "thanks for the suggestions. i've heard people talk about the \"vibe\" of those areas being different. when you say englewood or garfield park are \"less tourist friendly\" or \"higher crime,\" is that because of the demographics there or just the general economy? like, is it a specific kind of area i should be wary of?",
